{"tid":436152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新翠邨商場廁格發現屍體","createTime":"2017-10-15T02:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T02:12:52.000Z","uid":84436,"like":82,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b99386f8f3928d33071787c858d1c2bb6df062","tid":436152,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:21:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171015/57334057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171015%2F57334057&d=lIJcOy1SdpiccVNprGOqLTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5f074fce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171015%2F57334057&h=eb9e4785\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171015/57334057</a><br />\n<br />\n沙田大圍新翠邨商場，今早8時19分，一名老翁被發現在廁所廁格內昏迷不醒，救護員到場證實他當場死亡，警員正展開調查，並在死者身旁發現一份昨日的報紙，相信老翁昨日進入廁格後失救致死。"},{"pid":"96fe821150dcb3a7ec556eeed6e4c1c767b75e51","tid":436152,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:23:13.000Z","msg":"可能執尋日既報紙睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e235d84cafb9ae86f8fae5569bdb7cd2b69f59b","tid":436152,"uid":64345,"like":133,"dislike":0,"score":133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:24:17.000Z","msg":"飲完早茶，入廁所開大，死"},{"pid":"5254299b829fc30ddd5b980a7395270a18680c14","tid":436152,"uid":10692,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:25:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32945744890346a095a93b2bba64b775d83eacb9","tid":436152,"uid":11254,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:25:43.000Z","msg":"跑馬輸撚哂D錢心臟病死撚左"},{"pid":"7e59885ba7cc42d8340599f8aad1aa240d4e5677","tid":436152,"uid":49392,"like":105,"dislike":1,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"講起呢樣<br />\n商場廁格日頭真係成日爆<br />\n入面班人打飛機定玩電話，有次聽到入面揭緊報紙真係火都嚟"},{"pid":"4fc2fdcb97abecfcd3eb90ce728